      "content": "but you don't understand. it's not just a \"mistake.\" my entire identity was built on this work. without the work, there isn't actually a person here. there's just this empty, embarrassing shell of someone who wasted a decade chasing a ghost. it feels like the most honest thing i can do is just stop existing.",
